{"tid":254031,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知係咪一直單身, 我諗偏左","createTime":"2017-05-23T00:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T04:14:54.000Z","uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"acba03b7a8d8d6c71458c0b16a2e5fa255b05f4b","tid":254031,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:42:12.000Z","msg":"睇左比自己後生一個接一個咁拍拖, 我自卑、傷心又妒忌<br />\n我總係覺得自己值得擁有一段感情<br />\n我好想搵一個女朋友黎填補我心底嘅空缺, 雖然我知道咁樣係可能唔岩<br />\n因為一個女仔係一個人, 唔係一塊拼圖<br />\n感情係雙向, 需要互相尊重, 呵護, 珍惜, 唔係單單滿足自己<br />\n而且緣份冇得急亦不能創造<br />\n但係人越大, 越睇到自己身邊人一個個咁拍拖, 我就越在意自己心中嘅缺口<br />\n就好似砌拼圖少塊key piece要搵出黎一樣<br />\n聽完之後, 大家可能會恥笑我, 屌7我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 但感情唔抒發一下真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 有對象, 但係暫時冇咩行動, 一黎未諗到點追佢, 二黎未肯定自己會當係一個人定一個填補缺口嘅工具, 但係又好怕佢會比人追左, 當然更唔想佢原來一直有條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (如果是咁此post已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nSor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9d9da7f7cd66669c92f6040a77efc05253d48e","tid":254031,"uid":35931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:45:13.000Z","msg":"點解個利申好似我自己自白咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196b007d7f6db2a878d5ad30342ef20302c5b70b","tid":254031,"uid":14367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:49:20.000Z","msg":"當你妒忌其他人，就唔值得有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要既幸福唔係比較出黎<br />\n單身都可以好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c6e0c3807e92222012a51dd5de30348971080d","tid":254031,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你妒忌其他人，就唔值得有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要既幸福唔係比較出黎<br />\n單身都可以好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當我多年單身時, 我就羨慕有女朋友嘅<br />\n或者到我有女朋友時, 我又會羨慕番單身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但呢一刻我心中果個缺口無限放大緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d5679d086fa4156f0b83f2c2bba69e6c6b6ce4","tid":254031,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:45:30.000Z","msg":"搵PTGF/SP囉"},{"pid":"9459b39a1f658106e112b6fe9960f7ec7a87678b","tid":254031,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89e8a9483c0ff6ec7b49cb19bde36b34f35eb55","tid":254031,"uid":40536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:51:38.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5154030bad89b75e95c7b04493fd1827567941","tid":254031,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵PTGF/SP囉</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8036c42cc9385d63f5961a37948a9d3bf8e764c3","tid":254031,"uid":22775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:54:49.000Z","msg":"正常 人愈大愈認清呢個世界呢個社會 自然就會愈自卑"},{"pid":"c37b9ca5910b41336cc4f0f2affc3c42823be9d5","tid":254031,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:06:51.000Z","msg":"拍拖唔一定好<br />\n單身唔一定唔好<br />\n<br />\n拍拖真係唔係岩某d人<br />\n覺得好麻煩...<br />\n成日要哄女<br />\n日哄夜哄....<br />\n無哂自己時間...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申拍緊一年"},{"pid":"1d4fc9a93caa3441805f9af0f52e64a5580a20e5","tid":254031,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi